== 制作 ==
大部分拍攝在希臘的小島進行，包括[[斯科派洛斯島|斯科派洛斯島]]和[[斯基亞索斯島|斯基亞索斯島]]等，時間為2007年的8至9月<ref name=WPress/>，也有在希臘[[皮立翁山|皮立翁山]]邊的海濱小村{{tsl|en|Mouresi|莫雷遜}}拍攝。斯科派洛斯島的西岸卡斯塔尼海灘是主要場景<ref name=WPress/>，製作人員在此搭建了海灘酒吧和碼頭，在完成拍攝後拆卸<ref name="WPress">{{cite web| title = Mamma Mia! - Unfazed by the fuss in Skopelos| publisher = The Telegraph| date = 2008-07-15| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/artsandculture/2229868/Mamma-Mia---Unfazed-by-the-fuss-in-Skopelos.html| access-date = 2008-09-13| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100210055539/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/artsandculture/2229868/Mamma-Mia---Unfazed-by-the-fuss-in-Skopelos.html| archive-date = 2010-02-10| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。其餘部分在英國{{tsl|en|Pinewood Studios|松林制片廠}}拍攝，製作辦公室也設在該制片廠。此外，劇中唐娜的希臘別墅的全套家具都是在該制片廠內製造的。

皮雅斯·布士南所飾演的角色山姆·卡麥克有一段離開紐約辦公室並趕往去希臘小島的場景。該場景實際上是在英國[[倫敦市|倫敦市]][[萊姆街_(倫敦)|萊姆街]]的[[勞埃德大廈|勞埃德大廈]]拍攝，而在該處所出現的黃色出租車及紐約騎警則為增加真確性<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-news/sold-lloyds-of-london-hq-in-lime-street-to-go-for-290m-8300750.html |title = SOLD: Lloyd's of London HQ in Lime Street ‘to go for £290m’ |author = Evening Standard |date = 2012-11-09 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121119050907/https://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-news/sold-lloyds-of-london-hq-in-lime-street-to-go-for-290m-8300750.html |archivedate = 2012-11-19 }}</ref>。在電影內，[[史戴倫·史柯斯嘉|史戴倫·史柯斯嘉]]飾演的比爾·安德森所使用的遊艇（實際是[[雙桅小帆船|雙桅小帆船]]）是由[[黃埔船塢|黃埔船塢]]在1934年建造的，而該船名為「[[大帽山|大帽山]]」（TAI-MO-SHAN）<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.sandemanyachtcompany.co.uk/details/?id=233 |title = 45’ Teak Ketch 1933 - SOLD |author = Sandeman Yacht brokerage Poole |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095528/http://www.sandemanyachtcompany.co.uk/details/?id=233 |archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。另外，[[ABBA|ABBA]]成員[[班尼·安德森|班尼·安德森]]及[[比約恩·奧瓦爾斯|比約恩·奧瓦爾斯]]均有參與演出，其中班尼扮演漁夫並在戲內用鋼琴彈出《{{link-en|Dancing Queen (ABBA歌曲)|Dancing Queen|Dancing Queen}}》，而比約恩則在片後字幕時的片段內扮演手持[[七弦琴|七弦琴]]的希臘天神。

主角梅麗·史翠普在幼時曾接受[[歌劇|歌劇]]訓練，而後來她曾在《[[來自邊緣的明信片|來自邊緣的明信片]]》、《[[絲克伍事件|絲克伍事件]]》、《{{tsl|en|Death Becomes Her|捉神弄鬼}}》及《[[牧場之家好做伴|牧場之家好做伴]]》等電影內演唱<ref>{{cite web| title = Meryl Streep the singing and dancing queen - Telegraph Meryl| publisher = The Telegraph| date = 2008-07-04| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/arts/main.jhtml?xml=/arts/2008/07/04/bfmeryl104.xml| access-date = 2019-11-02| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080909130209/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/arts/main.jhtml?xml=%2Farts%2F2008%2F07%2F04%2Fbfmeryl104.xml| archive-date = 2008-09-09| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。[[九一一襲擊事件|九一一襲擊事件]]過後，她發現舞台劇《媽媽咪呀！》肯定了生命的價值，因而成為該舞台劇的粉絲<ref>Meryl Streep, speaking on 'Abba: The Mamma Mia Story', ITV</ref>。

