== 發布 ==
[[File:ABBA_2008_Av_Daniel_Åhs.jpg|thumb]]於2008年一同公開露面]]
2008年7月4日，ABBA成員比約恩·奧瓦爾斯、班尼·安德森、[[昂內塔·費爾特斯科格|昂內塔·費爾特斯科格]]和[[安妮-弗瑞德·林斯塔德|安妮-弗瑞德·林斯塔德]]參與了瑞典[[斯德哥爾摩|斯德哥爾摩]]的首映禮。該戲院由安德森擁有，當日是ABBA四名成員自1986年以來首次在公開場合同时被拍照<ref>{{cite web| author=Sandra Wejbro| title=ABBA återförenades på röda mattan (Swedish)| url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesliv/film/article2836959.ab| publisher=Aftonbladet| date=2008-07-04| accessdate=2008-07-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080711161437/http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesliv/film/article2836959.ab| archive-date=2008-07-11| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

而根據[[官方榜單公司|官方榜單公司]]的數據，電影在2008年11月成為了英國有史以來銷售最速的DVD，它在首日便售出了100萬份，並打破了之前由《[[鐵達尼號|鐵達尼號]]》所保持的56萬份紀錄<ref name="The Hollywood Reporter">{{Cite web |url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i17e8d113d82a5300a568d1520c7ee9ac |title = 'Mamma Mia!' breaks U.K. DVD record |author = Mark Sutherland |date = 2008-12-31 |publisher = The Hollywood Reporter |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090115195731/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i17e8d113d82a5300a568d1520c7ee9ac |archivedate = 2009-01-15 }}</ref>。而到了2008年底，官方榜單公司指電影的DVD已售出超過500萬份，宣布它已成為英國有史以來銷量最大的DVD，打破了之前由《[[加勒比海盗：黑珍珠号的诅咒|加勒比海盗：黑珍珠号的诅咒]]》所保持的470萬份紀錄，即平均每四個家庭中就有一個擁有該DVD<ref name="The Hollywood Reporter"/>。在美國，電影DVD發行的第一日便錄得3,000萬美元的收入<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/MAMMA-MIA-DVD-Takes-In-30-Million-In-First-Day-Of-Sales-20081217 |title = MAMMA MIA! DVD Takes In 30 Million In First Day Of Sales |author = BroadwayWorld.com |date = 2008-12-17 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181121094303/https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/MAMMA-MIA-DVD-Takes-In-30-Million-In-First-Day-Of-Sales-20081217 |archivedate = 2018-11-21 }}</ref>。而截止2008年12月31日，電影DVD成為了瑞典有史以來最暢銷的DVD，售出超過54萬份<ref>{{cite web|title=Nyheterna - tv4.se|url=http://nyheterna.se/1.799701/|publisher=nyheterna.se|accessdate=2020-09-13|archive-date=2011-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110809155519/http://www.nyheterna.se/1.799701/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反響 ==
=== 票房 ===
截至2009年1月23日，《媽媽咪呀！》在英國的票房收入為6,920萬英鎊，是英國史上票房收入最高的其中一部電影<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.25thframe.co.uk/chartspagetemplate.php?source=ukboxoffice |title = UK Highest Grossing Movies |author = 25thframe |date = 2011-02-09 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110215111058/http://www.25thframe.co.uk/chartspagetemplate.php?source=ukboxoffice |archivedate = 2011-02-15 }}</ref>。電影在英國開畫後奪得票房第一，496間戲院共錄得票房約660萬英鎊，並維持2星期票房冠軍，力壓[[迪士尼|迪士尼]]和[[皮克斯|皮克斯]]的《[[WALL-E|WALL-E]]》。而在希臘，電影在首映後首個周末票房奪得首位，票房收入達160萬美元<ref>{{cite news | title = Greece Box Office Index | publisher = Box Office Mojo | date = 2008-06-10 | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/greece/ | accessdate = 2008-06-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080517003040/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/intl/greece | archive-date = 2008-05-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在北美地區，電影首映票房為960萬美元，首映後首個周末的票房為2,700萬美元，排名第二，僅次於《[[黑暗騎士|黑暗騎士]]》。<ref>{{cite news | title = Box Office Mojo | publisher = Box Office Mojo | date = 2008-07-19 | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=mammamia.htm | accessdate = 2008-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100102050129/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=mammamia.htm | archive-date = 2010-01-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>；這使媽媽咪呀成為美國上映後首個周末票房最高的音樂劇電影，超越2007年的《[[髮膠明星夢|髮膠明星夢]]》<ref>{{cite web|author=|title=Variety.com-MAMMA MIA!|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117989593.html?categoryId=19&cs=1|publisher=Variety.com|date=2008-07-27|accessdate=2008-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919082630/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117989593.html?categoryId=19&cs=1|archive-date=2008-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，此紀錄被《[[魔法黑森林|魔法黑森林]]》所打破<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.playbill.com/news/article/into-the-woods-slides-into-second-place-in-domestic-box-office-totals-beating-unbroken-338152 |title = "Into the Woods" Slides Into Second Place in Domestic Box-Office Totals, Beating "Unbroken" |author = Michael Gioia, Vichet Chum |date = 2014-12-30 |publisher = Playbill |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190205211921/https://www.playbill.com/news/article/into-the-woods-slides-into-second-place-in-domestic-box-office-totals-beating-unbroken-338152 |archivedate = 2019-02-05 }}</ref>。

最終，《媽媽咪呀！》在北美的票房收入為1.441億美元，其他地區的票房收入合共為4.716億美元，全球總票房收入則為6.157億美元，而電影的拍攝預算為5200萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Mamma-Mia#tab=summary |title = Mamma Mia! (2008) |author = The Numbers |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200731153551/https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Mamma-Mia#tab=summary |archivedate = 2020-07-31 }}</ref>。在當時，電影成為了有史以來票房收入最高的真人音樂劇，直至2017年被[[比爾·坎登|比爾·坎登]]執導的《[[美女與野獸_(2017年電影)|美女與野獸]]》所打破。此電影亦是女性導演執導的最高票房電影，但同樣在2017年被[[派蒂·珍金斯|派蒂·珍金斯]]執導的《[[神力女超人_(2017年電影)|神力女超人]]》所打破<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.marketwatch.com/story/wonder-woman-passes-mamma-mia-as-highest-grossing-film-by-female-director-2017-06-23 |title = ‘Wonder Woman’ passes ‘Mamma Mia!’ as highest-grossing film by female director |author = Trey Williams |date = 2017-06-24 |publisher = Market Watch |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200219071323/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/wonder-woman-passes-mamma-mia-as-highest-grossing-film-by-female-director-2017-06-23 |archivedate = 2020-02-19 }}</ref>。

=== 影評 ===
影評人對該片評價不一。「[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]」統計在182個評論中有54%是正面，電影平均分為5.53（10分滿分）<ref name="rt">{{cite web | url=http://rottentomatoes.com/m/mamma_mia/ | title=Mamma Mia! Reviews | work=Rotten Tomatoes | publisher=Rotten Tomatoes | accessdate=2008-07-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080717180927/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/mamma_mia/ | archive-date=2008-07-17 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。爛番茄的影評為：「這部點唱機音樂劇充滿了蓬鬆的樂趣，但充滿著粗糙的歌聲及古怪搞笑的音調，可能不會讓你感到在整整90分鐘內「你可以跳舞」。」<ref name="rt"/>而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，根據37位評論家的評論，這部電影的平均分為51分（滿分100）<ref name="metacritic">{{Cite web |url = https://www.metacritic.com/movie/mamma-mia! |title = Mamma Mia! |author = Metacritic |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200711180753/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/mamma-mia! |archivedate = 2020-07-11 }}</ref>。在[[影院評分|影院評分]]所進行的民意調查內，電影的平均等級為A-（等級範圍是A+至F）<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cinemascore.com/ |title = Mamma Mia! |author = Cinemascore |date = 2008 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |archive-date = 2018-01-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180102130540/https://www.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》的雨果·里夫金德（Hugo Rifkind）給予四粒星（五粒星滿分），指劇中演員的表現很好，令電影予人一種輕鬆的感覺，又不需要過於認真地觀看<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article4245117.ece |title=Times Online |access-date=2008-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080917102728/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article4245117.ece |archive-date=2008-09-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。BBC廣播第五直播臺（BBC Radio 5 Live）的影評人馬克·科莫德（Mark Kermode）喜歡這部電影，不過亦批評電影的主調雖然是載歌載舞，但看起來卻像一班巨星喝醉酒在唱[[卡拉OK|卡拉OK]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=61UolzFTVPI |title=BBC 5 Live Kermode and Mayo Film Review |access-date=2008-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416130003/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=61UolzFTVPI |archive-date=2014-04-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而《[[衛報|衛報]]》的影評人彼得·布拉德肖（Peter Bradshaw）更為消極，只給予電影一顆星，直言在看完電影後「需要嘔吐」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/culture/2008/jul/10/film.reviews |title=Guardian Review |access-date=2008-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080927145040/http://www.guardian.co.uk/culture/2008/jul/10/film.reviews |archive-date=2008-09-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》則認為該片富娛樂性但略嫌混亂，又指找到這部電影完全是一件令人遺憾的事，但無論如何仍會再次觀看<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/arts/main.jhtml?xml=%2Farts%2F2008%2F07%2F11%2Fbfmamma111.xml |title=Telegraph review |access-date=2019-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080807022212/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/arts/main.jhtml?xml=%2Farts%2F2008%2F07%2F11%2Fbfmamma111.xml |archive-date=2008-08-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》的安吉·埃里格（Angie Errigo）則指電影可愛、乾淨並充滿陽光和趾尖<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/mamma-mia-review/ |title = Mamma Mia! Review |author = Angie Errigo |date = 2008-07-03 |publisher = Empire |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200913080333/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/mamma-mia-review/ |archivedate = 2020-09-13 }}</ref>。

另外，演員的唱功亦備受議論。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的喬丹·明澤（Jordan Mintzer）指部份演員（如[[梅麗·史翠普|梅麗·史翠普]]）似乎比其他明星（如[[皮尔斯·布鲁斯南|皮尔斯·布鲁斯南]]及[[斯特兰·斯卡斯加德|斯特兰·斯卡斯加德]]）更適合演出音樂喜劇<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://variety.com/VE1117937623.html |title = Mamma Mia! |author = Jordan Mintzer |date = 2008-07-05 |publisher = Variety |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081219094720/https://variety.com/VE1117937623.html |archivedate = 2008-12-19 }}</ref>。布鲁斯南的演出被很多影評人批評，他的歌喉分別被《[[紐約_(雜誌)|紐約]]》、《[[費城詢問報|費城詢問報]]》及《{{tsl|en|Miami Herald|邁阿密先驅報}}》批評像「水牛」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://nymag.com/movies/reviews/48514/index1.html |title = Bat Out of Hell |author = David Edelstein |date = 2008-07-11 |publisher = New York Magazine |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080716053110/https://nymag.com/movies/reviews/48514/index1.html |archivedate = 2008-07-16 }}</ref>、「驢叫」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.philly.com/inquirer/columnists/carrie_rickey/20080718__Mamma_Mia___here_we_go_again_-_this_time_on_screen.html |title = 'Mamma Mia,' here we go again - this time on screen |author = Carrie Rickey |date = 2008-07-18 |publisher = The Philadelphia Inquirer |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080725084341/http://www.philly.com/inquirer/columnists/carrie_rickey/20080718__Mamma_Mia___here_we_go_again_-_this_time_on_screen.html |archivedate = 2008-07-25 }}</ref>及「受傷的浣熊」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.miamiherald.com/1058/story/607314.html |title = Mamma Mia! (PG-13) **Â½ Singing! And dancing! Not much of a story! Who cares!?! |author = Rene Rodriguez |date = 2008-10-11 |publisher = Miami Herald |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081010232725/http://www.miamiherald.com/1058/story/607314.html |archivedate = 2008-10-10 }}</ref>。Creative Loafing的馬特·布倫森（Matt Brunson）指布鲁斯南「看起來很痛苦而且被歌詞噎住，就好比在相機前接受前列腺檢查一樣」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://charlotte.creativeloafing.com/gyrobase/out_of_tune/Content?oid=336031 |title = Out of tune - ABBA adaptation is summer's biggest disappointment |author = Matt Brunson |date = 2008-07-23 |publisher = Creative Loafing |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110616212436/http://charlotte.creativeloafing.com/gyrobase/out_of_tune/Content?oid=336031 |archivedate = 2011-06-16 }}</ref>。他更在2008年的第29届[[金酸莓奖|金酸莓奖]]评为最差男配角<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.mi6-hq.com/news/index.php?itemid=7371 |title = Pierce Brosnan lumped with `Worst Supporting Actor` Razzie |author = MI6-HQ.com |date = 2009-02-22 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-13 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200913083230/https://www.mi6-hq.com/news/index.php?itemid=7371 |archivedate = 2020-09-13 }}</ref>。

